The paper focuses on the implementation of collective communication operations in wide area computational systems, which involves distributed computing and networking. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing). The paper also discusses gathering network information and constructing logical clusters, which falls under the category of cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). Additionally, the paper deals with the heterogeneity of the environment, which is a common concern in cs.Distributed Systems. The paper also discusses performance modeling, which is relevant to cs.PF (Performance). Finally, the paper deals with constructing logical clusters, which is relevant to cs.SY (Systems and Control).
